00:02:19.874 --> 00:02:29.329
The more I let go of myself and my prerogatives, the less I try to grasp and hang on to things, the more alive I become.

00:02:29.469 --> 00:02:31.632
That's a basic biblical principle.

00:02:32.534 --> 00:02:37.361
Can I suggest, therefore, salvation has a lot to do with adventure?

00:02:38.543 --> 00:02:48.338
I don't want to sound trivial in saying that, but it's true, I think, that there's something adventurous about the saints, something safe

00:02:48.962 --> 00:02:53.809
